<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Candaar</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-02 23:01:34</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>just like to say, i got mine this afternoon. there was me (33 chanter), 41 mage, 44 druid, and we brought along a 50 wizzie for good measure. he didnt put up much of a fight.<BR>
<BR>
he is a pain even so. the ishva mal will dispell you at least once right of the pat, and he hits for about 60's. we just went in, i mes'd his pet, and we nuked the hell out of the ishva. went down pretty quickly. i camped him since the last big patch, and have killed him every time he spawned since then. his common drops are the spell of summon corpse (39th necro spell) and some sort of NO DROP brins, which im told are for some sort of paineel shield quest. i dont know the details on that.<BR>
<BR>
all i can say, is i love my robe. it looks awesome, and im glad to be out of the flock of FBR's (no offense, FBR is a good robe, just everyone and their alt has one)<BR>
<BR>
feel free to drop by if you want to take a peek. looks like insidious, but im told the blue is a slightly different shade. i thought it was identical, but who knows. <BR>
<BR>
ive only ever seen one other person wearing on of these, which makes me ever the more happier to have one.<BR>
<BR>
Candaar<BR>
